    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/ec062be07b39f9e68906d53c83ec9717.avif?t=1732895108\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br>在游戏中，你将踏上冒险之路，前往童话国度。通过完成拼图，你会获得更多的线索，逐渐了解这段感人故事背后所阐述的意义。爱、勇气和怜悯。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/659795e7bbac356ff9db3d1fce4b6bd6.poster.avif?t=1732895108\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/659795e7bbac356ff9db3d1fce4b6bd6.webm?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/659795e7bbac356ff9db3d1fce4b6bd6.mp4?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这必将是一场艰难却又让人铭记的旅程。旅途中，你将会结识善良的公主、正义的王子。你们将一路通行，通过无数考验，最终抵达终点。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/6a60361cf9cbc615a789d8c6414540bf.poster.avif?t=1732895108\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/6a60361cf9cbc615a789d8c6414540bf.webm?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/6a60361cf9cbc615a789d8c6414540bf.mp4?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/d0739234445754fac5327f48cf75109b.avif?t=1732895108\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br>游戏内的拼图灵感来源于彩绘玻璃，这是人类艺术史上最古老的艺术样式，几乎伴随着艺术史的产生而产生。彩绘玻璃艺术诞生于古希腊，在古希腊语中寓意“值得静思需要耐心的艺术工作”。正如其寓意，在你即将体验到的游戏中，你会看到一张张足以让人惊艳的艺术作品，而你需要付出些许的耐心，去再次重构这些艺术品。<br><br>你可以找一段空闲时间，带着女友或小孩一起凑在电脑前，一边闲聊饮茶，一边挪动鼠标，不紧不慢的摆弄、旋转每一块拼图，用最惬意的方式共同完成一副拼图，完成一段只属于你们的童话故事。、<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/bfb375cdb6c0c4561bd1db64007a3394.poster.avif?t=1732895108\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/bfb375cdb6c0c4561bd1db64007a3394.webm?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/bfb375cdb6c0c4561bd1db64007a3394.mp4?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/e731f0c77da4586f6b92b20ee3054621.avif?t=1732895108\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><br>在操作玩法上，你只需要控制鼠标，挪动拼图碎片，将其放置在正确的位置上。这很简单，但真正要考验你的，是思维逻辑以及空间构造能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/610f294ddb2edfe83eaae31f4c85d36a.poster.avif?t=1732895108\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/610f294ddb2edfe83eaae31f4c85d36a.webm?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/610f294ddb2edfe83eaae31f4c85d36a.mp4?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏内关卡数量多达五十，每个关卡内的拼图各不相同。假如这是一场旅行，那这些关卡就是各不相同的景点，你们会在旅途中一一相遇。除此外，游戏共有四个难度，可以任意选择，不同的难度将决定关卡碎片的数量。这会让你的旅途更加充满乐趣，即便是重回你所经过的地方，仍旧能看到不同的风景。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/1f9cabde78960d796b9d713c3a6134de.poster.avif?t=1732895108\" width=610 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/1f9cabde78960d796b9d713c3a6134de.webm?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1034150/extras/1f9cabde78960d796b9d713c3a6134de.mp4?t=1732895108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在难度推荐上，我们更建议大家先从“极简单”难度开始入手 ，这会让你的旅途逐渐由简到难，充满乐趣。当然，如果你是喜欢挑战性的玩家，可以选择“正常”模式。",
